distribute-desc: COCKTAIL(COCK) will be distributed in the spirit of YFI: there is no pre-mine, no founder shares, no VC interests - simply equal-opportunity staking distribution to attract a broad and vision-aligned community to steward the future of the protocol and token. COCK is built on the TRON network.
res-how-mine: You will need TronLink to mine COCK. Choose your favorite cocktail and click on ‘Stake’. Wait for a few seconds and you will see the ‘Success’ notice.
why-aboout-regarding: Why are there delays in updating the numbers
res-why-aboout-regarding: On opening the website, the website will try to talk with TronLink to get the numbers. Tronlink itself has delays in displaying the assets, the website can only show updated numbers once Tronlink is updated.
res-how-calculated: It’s equally distributed through time. For example, each hour USDJ pool generates
re-governance: The rest of the COCK token would be locked in the contract and entirely governed by COCK holders, for example, vote for adding more distribution pools.
re-Development-fund: In order to maintain the project and bring more pools & features, 10% of all mined COCK token rewards will be set aside for the development fund.
re-distribution-timetable: The total supply of COCK token is fixed at 10,000 with no extra supply. All tokens will be distributed to miners within 12 weeks.
re-when-begin: For the first round, the #USDJ, #JFI and #TRX begins on 20th Sep 2020 2:00 PM UTC time
how-long-last: How long will the mining last
re-how-long-last: Each round lasts for 28 days since it starts. There are three rounds in total. While for #COCK/TRX pool, it lasts for 56 days since it starts from the second round
